            Have a biomechanics challenge? Building something at the intersection of AI and human movement? We'd love to hear about it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/[0.03] p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06]">
          <div class="text-center mb-10">
